name: CNTRCT_PBP_SK
comment: AN IDR ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A VERSION OF A CONTRACT.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_EFCTV_SK
comment: AN IDR ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A VERSION OF A CONTRACT.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_SK_EFCTV_DT
comment: CONTRACT VERSION EFFECTIVE DATE.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_SK_OBSLT_DT
comment: CONTRACT VERSION OBSOLETE DATE.

name: CNTRCT_NUM
comment: A NUMBER UNIQUELY IDENTIFYING A MANAGED CARE ORGANIZATION (MCO) OR PRESCRIPTION DRUG PLAN (PDP) THAT PROVIDES COVERAGE TO ELIGIBLE MEDICARE BENEFICIARIES.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_NUM
comment: A NUMBER UNIQUELY IDENTIFYING A PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE (PBP) OFFERED WITHIN A MANAGED CARE ORGANIZATION (MCO) OR PRESCRIPTION DRUG PLAN (PDP) CONTRACT.

name: CNTRCT_PMT_STUS_CD
comment: CONTRACT PAYMENT STATUS.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_PMT_STUS_BGN_DT
comment: DATE THE PAYMENT STATUS IS EFFECTIVE.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_PMT_STUS_END_DT
comment: DATE THE PAYMENT STATUS IS TERMINATED.

name: CNTRCT_ENRLMT_STUS_CD
comment: ENROLLMENT STATUS INTO THE CONTRACT.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_ENRLMT_STUS_BGN_DT
comment: DATE THE STATUS IS EFFECTIVE.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_ENRLMT_STUS_END_DT
comment: DATE THE PBP ELECTION STARTED.  FOR PART D PBPS THIS DATE IDENTIFIES WHEN THE PART D ENROLLMENT BECAME EFFECTIVE FOR THE PART D CONTRACT .

name: CNTRCT_EGHP_CD
comment: CONTRACTS EMPLOYER GROUP HEALTH PLAN CODE.

name: CNTRCT_PACE_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A TYPE OF PROGRAM OF ALL-INCLUSIVE CARE FOR THE ELDERLY (PACE) PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE (PBP) PLAN.    REFERENCE TABLE: CNTRCT_PACE_TYPE_CD

name: CNTRCT_DRUG_PLAN_IND_CD
comment: A FIELD THAT INDICATES WHETHER A SPECIFIC PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE OFFERS PART D COVERAGE.  Y = PLAN IS A DRUG PLAN (HAS PART D BENEFIT)  N = PLAN IS NOT A DRUG PLAN

name: CNTRCT_REINSRNC_CD
comment: INDICATION OF THE PLAN PARTICIPATING IN THE REINSURANCE DEMONSTRATION.  VALID VALUES ARE BLANK - NOT PARTICIPATING, 1  - 1A,     2 - 1B,    3 - 2

name: CNTRCT_PBP_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE DESCRIBING THE TYPE OF PLAN.

name: CNTRCT_SPCL_PLAN_IND_CD
comment: INDICATOR FOR SPECIAL NEEDS PLAN.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_STUS_CD
comment: PBP STATUS.  VALID VALUE IS A = ACTIVE. MARX WILL SET THE VALUE TO I = INACTIVE, WHEN THERE IS NO SUBSEQUENT RECORD FOR THE SAME PBP.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_PTD_BNFT_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING WHICH OF THE FOUR STATUTORILY DEFINED TYPES OF PART D BENEFITS A PLAN CAN OFFER.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_EMPLR_CY_IND_CD
comment: INDICATION OF EMPLOYER CALENDAR YEAR.

name: CNTRCT_EMPLR_PLAN_IND_CD
comment: INDICATES IF A PLAN IS ONLY OFFERED TO EMPLOYER GROUPS.  APPLIES TO LOCAL AND REGIONAL MA CONTRACTS AND PDPS.    0 = PLAN IS NOT EMPLOYER GROUP ONLY  1 = PLAN IS OPEN ONLY TO EMPLOYER GROUPS

name: CNTRCT_PBP_BSF_WTHDRWL_AMT
comment: THE AMOUNT WITHDRAWN FROM THE BENEFICIARY STABILIZATION FUND.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_BSF_WTHLD_AMT
comment: THE AMOUNT WITHHELD FROM THE BENEFICIARY STABILIZATION FUND.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_BGN_DT
comment: THE START DATE OF THE PBP CONTRACT.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_END_DT
comment: THE END DATE OF THE PBP CONTRACT.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_NAME
comment: TEXT LABEL DESCRIBING THE PBP, USUALLY THE PRODUCT NAME.

name: CNTRCT_PBP_REDSGNTN_DT
comment: PLAN REDESIGNATION EFFECTIVE DATE.

name: META_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND A 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT INITIALLY LOADED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS LOADED INTO THE IDR.    REFERENCE TABLE: V2_MDCR_META_DCTNRY_SRC

name: CNTRCT_FRMLRY_ID
comment: A UNIQUE IDENTIFIER ASSIGNED TO EACH NEWLY CREATED FORMULARY.  (DDL_20090320_2)

name: CNTRCT_PBP_BGN_YR_NUM
comment: THE YEAR IS THE BEGINNING OF THE LEGAL PERIOD THAT THE PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE (PBP) CAN OPERATE AS AN ENTITY THAT PROVIDES BENEFITS TO THE BENEFICIARY.  THE PLAN/PROVIDER SIGNS A ONE YEAR CONTRACT THAT ALLOWS IT TO LEGALLY PROVIDE BENEFITS TO MEDICARE BENEF

name: CNTRCT_PBP_PLAN_TYPE_DESC
comment: A STANDARD DESCRIPTION OF A PLAN TYPE (FOR EXAMPLE: ENHANCED ALTERNATIVE PLAN, MEDICARE-ONLY PACE PLAN, ETCÅ¨

name: CNTRCT_PBP_EFCTV_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE STATUS OF AN ENTRY FOR A PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE (PBP) PLAN.  VALID VALUES:  1 = CURRENT  0 = HISTORICAL

name: META_LST_UPDT_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT UPDATED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_LTST_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_LST_UPDT_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS UPDATED IN THE IDR.

name: CNTRCT_DENMNS_PLAN_IND
comment: AN IDENTIFIER USED TO INDICATE IF A PLAN MEETS DE MINIMIS CRITERIA. [CME CONTRACT]

name: CNTRCT_STD_PLAN_TYPE_NAME
comment: A STANDARD DESCRIPTION OF THE PLAN TYPE THAT IS PART OF THE PLAN NAME

name: CNTRCT_PTD_TYPE
comment: A DERIVED VALUE BASED ON CONTRACT NUMBER WHICH IDENTIFIES THE TYPE OF CONTRACT.  VALID VALUES:    EMPL  PDP  MAPD  POS

name: CNTRCT_PLAN_ALOW_ASGNMT_CD
comment: INDICATES IF THE PLAN/PBP HAS MET THE CRITERIA FOR BEING ALLOWED TO ACCEPT AUTO-ENROLLEES.

name: CNTRCT_PLAN_MA_REASGN_CD
comment: IDENTIFIES IF REASSIGNMENT OF LIS BENEFICIARIES IS NECESSARY FOR THE NEXT CONTRACT YEAR

name: CNTRCT_PLAN_PTD_BNFT_CD
comment: THE CODE THAT IDENTIFIES WHICH OF THE FOUR STATUTORILY DEFINED TYPES A PART D PLAN CAN OFFER.

name: CNTRCT_PLAN_REASGNMT_CD
comment: IDENTIFIER FOR A VALID REASSIGNMENT STATUS.

name: CNTRCT_PLAN_SBSDY_STUS_CD
comment: INDICATES IF A PLAN SUBSIDIZES THE PREMIUM FOR THE EMPLOYER BENEFICIARIES IN THE PLAN.

name: CNTRCT_CMMI_PTD_PMT_MODEL_SW
comment: INDICATES IF A PLAN IS PART OF THE CMMI PART D PAYMENT MODEL

name: CNTRCT_CMMI_PTD_SNRSM_SW
comment: INDICATES IF A PLAN HAS APPROVED PART D SENIOR SAVINGS
